text: Beskidian Foothills or Beskidian Piedmont may refer to: * West Beskidian Foothills, a foothill region, adjacent to the Western Beskids * Central Beskidian Foothills, a foothill region, adjacent to the Central Beskids * Beskidian Southern Foothills, a foothill region of the Central Beskids == See also == * Central Beskids (disambiguation) * Eastern Beskids (disambiguation) * Beskid (disambiguation)
title: Beskidian Foothills
